  /- Consider `rf` and `rg` such that `f` and `g` have power series expansion on the disks
    of radius `rf` and `rg`. -/
  rcases hg with ‚ü®rg, Hg‚ü©
  rcases hf with ‚ü®rf, Hf‚ü©
